{"tid":1530501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[高記仔入黎]曾偉雄、張建宗母校有警察拎長盾係茶記門口塞住今日去聲援嘅師兄","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:36:05.000Z","uid":33775,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9642c1906fdc8ee6e07ea05c7ffb8e7ac19c8c","tid":1530501,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKOYtKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKOYtKU.jpg&h=f823f52e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n成件事係今朝有人係學校門口鳩叫支持師弟<br />\n真係淨係鳩叫之後就走左<br />\n之後完左早會就想去附近嘅東方茶餐廳食野<br />\n諗住接埋師弟放學 (第一日開學10點幾就放)<br />\n食到一半門口有狗排盾陣唔比人出去 一出去就拉<br />\n之後門口聚集左成30隻狗<br />\n圖中個吳兆康係區議員黎　都係舊生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成件事冇組織過真係自發活動，亦都冇集結，只係叫左陣就散水去食野。間茶記重要行１０分鐘左右先到，點解ｄ狗識去捉人，好明顯學校有仆街報警拉鳩自己舊生。</span></span>"},{"pid":"1272de538bf320589780f734082fe0da1b12f66d","tid":1530501,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/a.1003686762991871/3178861772141015/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fphotos%2Fa.1003686762991871%2F3178861772141015%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=21bf1612\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/a.1003686762991871/3178861772141015/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"5f52c32c39d11313c79300344e8b6e0b9d267c3e","tid":1530501,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e4b0d51f2bbe1bc0103e38f006ea0946adfdf0","tid":1530501,"uid":81477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:35:41.000Z","msg":"堅道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd6cb4fecc08f089005f